    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Order containing 16 species in one family of stocky, pigeon-like ground birds with short legs, fast flight, and feeding upon seeds and insects in the deserts of Africa and Asia.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
